    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"340\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/ipr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=340&amp;height=246\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646266/ipr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"386\" data-width=\"533\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646297\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"ipr.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646266\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"fc6d09dc-688b-4d51-aa3d-5f165d538534\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/ipr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=533&amp;height=386 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/ipr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152444&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=340&amp;height=246 1x\"></span><p>You can add a RenderMan IPR ROP from the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544643009/RenderMan+Shelf\" rel=\"nofollow\">RenderMan Shelf</a> or from the /out pane.</p><h3 id=\"Setup-UsingRenderManShelf\">Using RenderMan Shelf</h3><p>We can use the ROP tool in the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544643009/RenderMan+Shelf\" rel=\"nofollow\">RenderMan Shelf</a> to create a ROP that automatically adds an integrator VOP to your RIS Network.</p><h3 id=\"Setup-Usingoutpane(ManualConfiguration)\">Using out pane (Manual Configuration)</h3><h4 id=\"Setup-AddRenderMANIPRROP\">Add RenderMAN IPR ROP</h4><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"350\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/risipr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152604&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=350&amp;height=360\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646266/risipr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152604&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646300\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"risipr.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646266\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"2b4eed0f-5d62-4253-8552-99c7c29df283\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/risipr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152604&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=404&amp;height=416 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/risipr.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152604&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=350&amp;height=360 1x\"></span> </p><h4 id=\"Setup-AddIntegrator\">Add Integrator</h4><p>In your RIS Network, add an integrator VOP inside your RIS Network, e.g.<strong> </strong><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661775\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrPathTracer</a></p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"346\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/rfhintegrator.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152230&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=346&amp;height=296\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646266/rfhintegrator.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152230&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"371\" data-width=\"433\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646282\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfhintegrator.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646266\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c5a6691e-e536-4cb2-96e4-748c82cb9d49\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/rfhintegrator.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152230&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=433&amp;height=371 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/rfhintegrator.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152230&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=346&amp;height=296 1x\"></span><h4 id=\"Setup-SettheIntegrator\">Set the Integrator</h4><p>Simply drag the path of your integrator VOP path to the <strong>Integrator</strong> in RenderMan RIS ROP.  If you skip this step, by default, it will use the PxrPathTracer integrator with its default parameters.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/withintegrator.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152443&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=275\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646266/withintegrator.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152443&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646294\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"withintegrator.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646266\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f5d5f753-e78d-4d76-be22-0b524385d5e5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/withintegrator.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152443&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=720&amp;height=331 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646266/withintegrator.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433152443&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=600&amp;height=275 1x\"></span> </p>"
